// Epilogue stuff
COPY ~golden_horse/2da/rqrev.2da~ ~override/rqrev.2da~
  REPLACE ~99999~ ~Revan Artecratos went back to Amn and rejoined his Golden Horse mercenary company. In time the mercenary company grew into such size and importance that even Council of Five started to regard Revan as threat. This prompted Revan to split up of his company to several smaller units. Afterwards he left Amn and went back to Moonsea but his "friends" of old "Those who Harp" tried to settle some old scores. Returning back to Amn but not really content there he moved to Rasheman to found fortified monastery as his retirement home.~ // @99999
EXTEND_TOP ~ar6200.bcs~ ~golden_horse/baf/rqar6200.baf~

