COPY ~golden_horse/itm/rqclck01.itm~ ~override/rqclck01.itm~
/* Unidentified name */
SAY NAME1 ~Cloak~
/* Identified name */
SAY NAME2  ~Cloak of Magical Absorption~
SAY UNIDENTIFIED_DESC
~Magical cloak of unidentified magical properties.~
SAY DESC
~Cloak of Magical Absorption
Krulomo originally created this magic as part of a golem-making project, but later reworked it into a cloak. Why he parted with the cloak is not known. One scholar from Sembia has suggested that, while powerful, it is still a charged item, and so Krulomo sold it to recoup part of his costs.

STATISTICS:
Weight: 2 lbs

Abilities: Trap Spell
   Duration: 8 hours or until 30 spell levels have been trapped
   Use: One charge per use

Usable by:
Mages (Single-class,Multi-class,Dual-class)
Bards
Sorcerers
~

/* ----------------------------------------- Helmets -----------------------------------------*/

//Star of spell Sequencing   -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
COPY ~golden_horse/itm/rqisto01.itm~ ~override/rqisto01.itm~
/* Unidentified name */
SAY NAME1 ~Ioun Stone~
/* Identified name */
SAY NAME2  ~Star of Spell Sequencing~ //~Ioun Stone of protection~
SAY UNIDENTIFIED_DESC
~This is a small stone that floats in an orbit around the owner's head.  Simply equip the stone to set it in its orbit.  These obviously magical stones have different properties depending on their color.~
SAY DESC
~Star of Spell Sequencing
You call this useful?! After I use up spells it doesn't do anything! Chroniclers record Bruno chastising his enchanter for Ring of spell sequencing. So Julich the enchanter created this ioun stone which additionally protects wearer from harm. Ring of spell sequencing the original precursor to this artifact does not survive but Ioun Stone "Star" does and it has changed ownership many times since then. However due to shortcuts taken by Julich the artifact requires certain amount of Intelligence.


STATISTICS:
Wight: 2 lbs

Equipped Abilities:
Armor Class:  +2 bonus
Saving Throws:  +2 bonus

Special Abilities:
Spell Sequencer once per day
Spell Trigger once per day
Contigency once per day

Usable By:
  Mages (Single-class,Multi-class,Dual-class)
  Intelligence at least 16
~

//Ioun stone of elemental protection   -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
COPY ~golden_horse/itm/rqisto02.itm~ ~override/rqisto02.itm~
/* Unidentified name */
SAY NAME1 ~Ioun Stone~
/* Identified name */
SAY NAME2  ~Ioun Stone of Elemental Protection~
SAY UNIDENTIFIED_DESC
~This is a small stone that floats in an orbit around the owner's head.  Simply equip the stone to set it in its orbit.  These obviously magical stones have different properties depending on their color.~
SAY DESC
~Ioun Stone of Elemental Protection
Imarmann as part of the deposit had received services of enchanter and first thing he was ordered to create was series of ioun stones one of them was was this Ioun stone of elemental protection. Unlike other artifacts ioun stones made for Imarmann do not have much of a history. Imarmann himself had used them sparingly. Scholars only known records are above mentioned of contract and Imarmann accounting records. The stone then was auctioned off by successive merchant company.


STATISTICS:
