/* Unidentified name */
SAY NAME1 ~Tome~
/* Identified name */
SAY NAME2  ~Book of the Dead~
SAY UNIDENTIFIED_DESC
~An ornate, leather-bound tome. The tome is of very unusual design. Each side has two screws penetrating each corner of the book. Functioning as bookmark but forcing the book to be opened only on one page.~
SAY DESC
~Book of the Dead
The famed book of the Dead. This apparently lesser copy is secured in such way so it can only open the page with Animate Dead spell. Why did the makers bothered to make this tome while limiting to display only pages on Animate Dead spell is unclear to you.

STATISTICS:
